objects.description: FIN5 maintains access to victim environments by using Valid Accounts Mitigation to access External Remote Services Mitigation as well as establishing a backup RDP tunnel by using FLIPSIDE. (Citation: Mandiant FIN5 GrrCON Oct 2016)
